query:
SELECT legacyLocationId, location, sliceNumber, angleDeg, stationKey, componentGroup
FROM tmlReadings
WHERE inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber = '54-11-001')
AND legacyLocationId = '9'
ORDER BY angleDeg
LIMIT 10;
